title: CAN_REQUEST_ASSETS_FOR_CUTSCENE_ENTITY
content:
0xB56BBBCC2955D9CB0xDD8878E9// CanRequestAssetsForCutsceneEntity
BOOL CAN_REQUEST_ASSETS_FOR_CUTSCENE_ENTITY();Returns: Whether you can request assets for cutscene entities, like components.Returns when it is safe to start applying changes to cutscene entities.Should always be used for applying components.See SET_CUTSCENE_PED_COMPONENT_VARIATION_FROM_PED and REGISTER_ENTITY_FOR_CUTSCENE for an example.This will be true before the cutscene is considered loaded
